Food is above average.  The drink are extremely expensive and so is the food.  I recommend don't even stop by.  The waiters are fast and attentive but for a 2 coke colas it's €15 and for two sangrias it's €23.  I would go somewhere else.  We had the seafood paella and the huevos estrillados con jamon iberico.  It was good but they are over priced!
